<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Lehman starts BMC as buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Lehman starts BMC as buy.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Lehman Brothers said analyst Brian Skiba initiated coverage of BMC Software with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- said set a 12-month price target of $70.</p>
<p>-- said estimated revenue growth of 25 percent to 30 percent for fiscal year 1998, adding strong indirect reseller channels and OEM relationships should continue to help push sales.</p>
<p>BMC Software rose 1-7/16 to 55-3/4 in late-morning trading.</p>
